 class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcdbe2bec6a44a0ffa267dca07b64ec89a5e9b0a","tid":347084,"uid":61228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:52:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/04/214856_89c160b7ca17a627a36f30a4984e8c64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F04%2F214856_89c160b7ca17a627a36f30a4984e8c64.jpg&h=f7f985d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我呀爺都比左隻呢d牙我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無話係咩牙呀</blockquote><br />\n呢隻似狼狗牙，雜食動物"},{"pid":"d43bd10b08506471f92cb3851c8a2ffc4c1d411b","tid":347084,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:53:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>比例來計應該係上牙，1比1.5左右<br />\n不過牙尖打磨過冇哂血槽</blockquote><br />\n應該係左邊既牙<br />\n因為後面同右邊都有凹槽</blockquote><br />\n虎牙應該就雙血槽，你呢隻條血槽唔明顯而得一條<br />\n我自己才藝粗淺唔敢講，以前有望狼牙<br />\n你隻牙太對稱太完美</blockquote><br />\n希望唔係鄉下啲流浪狗既牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12917e435032946fa54a665a8773a76a076f3c5c","tid":347084,"uid":61228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:54:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>比例來計應該係上牙，1比1.5左右<br />\n不過牙尖打磨過冇哂血槽</blockquote><br />\n應該係左邊既牙<br />\n因為後面同右邊都有凹槽</blockquote><br />\n虎牙應該就雙血槽，你呢隻條血槽唔明顯而得一條<br />\n我自己才藝粗淺唔敢講，以前有望狼牙<br />\n你隻牙太對稱太完美</blockquote><br />\n希望唔係鄉下啲流浪狗既牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n隻牙幾大，虎牙有八到十cm"},{"pid":"65e5c84573f213ef99b2c154e4dd5ba3d7401247","tid":347084,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:55:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/04/214856_89c160b7ca17a627a36f30a4984e8c64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservi